PR DESCRIPTION:
## Fixes issue

<!-- If your PR fixes an open issue, use `Fixes #ISSUE_NUMBER` to link your PR with the issue. -->

Fixes #1086 

## Changes proposed
- get rid of second version of preferences package/classes in module Gui
- hide implementation of preference reading/writing from rest of application, using an interface allows other kind of implementation without changing the usage
- move methods not directly belonging to the storage of settings into new classes (GET.jobs and encryption of SpotifyToken)
- replace calls to AppSettings.GET and AppSettings.SET by just calling AppSettings
- have getters and setters in same class
- better understandable names

<!-- List all the proposed changes in your PR -->

